skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: restaurant finder
des: This skill randomly selects a restaurant within a 5-6 mile radius of you and will speak it to you. The skill will only select restaurants that are open.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
